Installation Order

We'll install tools in the order they are used by the pipeline.

Step 1 — Java

Jenkins and Maven require Java.

sudo apt update

sudo apt install openjdk-21-jdk -y

Verify

java -version
Step 2 — Git
sudo apt install git -y

Verify

git --version
Step 3 — Maven
sudo apt install maven -y

Verify

mvn -version
Step 4 — Docker

Install Docker.

Verify

docker --version

Add ubuntu user to docker group

sudo usermod -aG docker ubuntu
Step 5 — Jenkins

Install Jenkins.

Verify

systemctl status jenkins

Open

http://<EC2-Public-IP>:8080
Step 6 — Trivy

Install Trivy.

Verify

trivy --version
